thread.title_full: Pool Supplies Superstore reviewed by Steven Campos

author: Steven Campos
title: Steven Campos
text: Pool Supply Superstore, was the only store to have what I needed in Stock and it beat the price of every local competitor I found. the shipping was free for my order which made this even more wonderfully convenient and the free shipping came quick. I was super happy with this store.
